      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions (inlet velocity profile, fluid temperature, hematocrit) documented with uncertainty bands and traceable to NIST-calibrated instruments.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity and temperature are documented with NIST-traceable calibration. Hematocrit uncertainty is reported but calibration traceability for the hematocrit sensor is incomplete, reducing achieved level."
