      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E_rms) computed for velocity field and hemolysis index with experimental uncertainty propagated; statistical significance demonstrated.",
      "rationale": "E_rms computed for velocity field with uncertainty bands. Hemolysis index comparison uses mean absolute error without full uncertainty propagation on experimental side, limiting achieved level to 3."
