      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI (normalized index of hemolysis, wall shear stress distribution) directly maps to clinical risk endpoints specified in the device submission requirements.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis is directly linked to clinical endpoints. Wall shear stress is reported but its mapping to thrombus risk endpoints is described qualitatively rather than quantitatively."
